abstract: Rolling Stones begin 15-city ZIP Code North America tour in San Diego's Petco Park with concert of songs spanning their long history, joined by guitarist Gary Clark Jr and chamber choir from California State University at Long Beach,
lead_paragraph: The Rolling Stones kicked off their 15-city “ZIP Code” North American tour in San Diego on Sunday night

headline.main: Rolling Stones Start Themselves Up in San Diego
